gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString:
Contains metadata and quality information on the Australian Regional GPS Network (ARGN), the South Pacific Regional GPS Network (SPRGN) and other permanent GPS stations across Australia, which are observed on a non continuous basis.
Metadata information for each tracking stations contains data such as the site name, connection type, location, position, equipment and their serial numbers, main contact agencies, etc.
The site quality database contains statistical quantities for each site for each day of year.
